<h2 class="heading-subtitle">5) Harold Wilson</h2><p class="paragraph-text"><strong>1964-1970, Labour</strong></p><p class="paragraph-text">Yorkshire-born Labour politician, Harold Wilson, was best known for enacting social reforms in education, health, housing, gender equality and child poverty, among other social issues.</p>

<figure>
    
        <img
            loading="lazy"
