<h2 class="heading-subtitle">9) John Major</h2><p class="paragraph-text"><strong>1990-1997, Conservative</strong></p><p class="paragraph-text">John Major is best known for beginning the Northern Ireland Peace Process, and for reviving the country&#x27;s economic growth.</p><p class="paragraph-text">During his time, Major survived an IRA attack on Number 10, and took a leading role alongside President George Bush in the first Gulf War.</p>

<figure>
    
        <img
            loading="lazy"
            alt="Tony Blair was Prime Minister from 1997 to 2007"
