    </span>
</figcaption>

</figure>

<h2 class="heading-subtitle">15) Liz Truss</h2><p class="paragraph-text"><strong>2022-present, Conservative</strong></p><p class="paragraph-text"><a href="/news/liz-truss-confirmed-prime-minister/">Liz Truss beat Rishi Sunak</a> to become the British prime minister. She has so far made big pledges to cut down energy bills and tax.</p>
    

    

    

